<item>
            <title>[LU-18189] Improve checkpatch-man.pl functionality</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18189</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are still many improvements to be made for the &lt;b&gt;checkpatch-man.pl&lt;/b&gt; script. Some of the main improvements to be done are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add options similar to what &lt;b&gt;checkpatch.pl&lt;/b&gt; currently has&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Improve the subject version command (add the git tags)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Improve message clarity for users&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Improve context surrounding the checks so fewer false positives exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;As new pages are made, it is certain that the script will require modifications to catch new edge cases&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that patches relating to this ticket should use &lt;b&gt;Test-Parameters: trivial&lt;/b&gt; to avoid overloading the test system&lt;/p&gt;</description>
